        "content": "<p>We are migrating these dropdows from using bootstrap supported dropdowns to use tippy. Would it be cleaner to move the <code>[Disable]</code> buttons (which also have bad contrast ratio to background color) inside the dropdown?</p>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/17/00YNkpwHYUeOoQ02tkIJTLFL/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/17/00YNkpwHYUeOoQ02tkIJTLFL/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/17/00YNkpwHYUeOoQ02tkIJTLFL/image.png\"></a></div>",
        "id": 1608726,
        "sender_full_name": "Aman (amanagr)",
        "timestamp": 1689229087
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It would be an option like <code>Direct Message</code> in compose box.<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/2/aa/IPZ1uIqdkZf98hP2SwcE8qFM/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/aa/IPZ1uIqdkZf98hP2SwcE8qFM/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/aa/IPZ1uIqdkZf98hP2SwcE8qFM/image.png\"></a></div>",
        "id": 1608727,
        "sender_full_name": "Aman (amanagr)",
        "timestamp": 1689229143
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Also, a button presented as a link enclosed in brackets is funny to look at.</p>",
        "id": 1608728,
        "sender_full_name": "Aman (amanagr)",
        "timestamp": 1689229203
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"5140\">Aman (amanagr)</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/101-design/topic/Migrating.20org.20settings.20dropdowns.20to.20tippy/near/1608728\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Also, a button presented as a link enclosed in brackets is funny to look at.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Agreed. I'd definitely like to see and play with this as an option inside the dropdown.</p>",
        "id": 1608978,
        "sender_full_name": "Karl Stolley",
        "timestamp": 1689255323
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Cool! Thanks for the feedback.</p>",
        "id": 1609032,
        "sender_full_name": "Aman (amanagr)",
        "timestamp": 1689260382
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Yeah, the \"disable\" option has always felt a bit weird and is kinda ugly, and it'll be great to be able to clean that up.</p>",
