        "sender_full_name": "Tim Abbott",
        "timestamp": 1689261333
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Also, IMO the dropdown shouldn't cover the input field -- check out the screenshot. But I think this is irrelevant to migrating them to Tippy.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/94/nIXTQWqm1SL-H-q3XXbr8Zmx/image.png\">Edit Bot Form</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/94/nIXTQWqm1SL-H-q3XXbr8Zmx/image.png\" title=\"Edit Bot Form\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/94/nIXTQWqm1SL-H-q3XXbr8Zmx/image.png\"></a></div>",
